### Get all books (Should be empty at first)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

###

### Create a new book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Fellowship of the Ring",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "isbn": "978-0261153573",
  "publishedYear": 1957
}
